column3: Built up system 0018, all sensors worked, except Baro LWR & SWR.  Swapped MET, Serial board, but LWR & SWR still not working.  Could have been issue, current limiting issue with SW Rad.  Finally swapped CPU board, and LWR & SWR finally fixed and functional.
Iridium SIM card installed.  All sensors tested okay.  All functions tested okay, RF modem & Irdium xmit successful.  Needs current drain testing.
Ran Current drain test, 14.57mA Average.  Dumped FLASH RAM data file, which looked okay.
Updated Iridium 1st transmit time to 00:41.  Upated firmware to version 2.01, 170530.
Ran Current drain test for 8 days (over Xmas Holiday), 14.02mA Average.  Dumped FLASH RAM data file, which looked okay.
Successfully tested GPS and Iridium XMIT test outside.
